Bilal,
It has always been and will always be only ever you. 

Of everything that was said tonight, these are the words that are imprinted on my heart.  And they are your words:

I saw us, with kids, happy and in love. Spending time with our children in a big back garden, running around. Having our family surround us with love. Us being married and in so much love! Not a care in the world, it was just us. Nothing else mattered. We were so happy! Grew old together and watched our kids grow to be amazingly independent, strong loving adults ð¥°ð Itâs like all of those emotions from our future came rushing back to me.

Those are the important words that I took away from tonight. 

Call it fate, destiny, kismet, red string, our Angel, true love, soulmate, or what ever you want: but the significant item is that Bilal & Genevieve belong together.
